title: Cheesy Stuffed Chicken & Butter Crushed Potatoes Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! This chicken breast is hiding a delicious secret, can you guess what it is? Slice it open to reveal the gooey centre, a mouthwatering mix of spinach, onion and lots of molten Cheddar cheese. Paired with crushed potatoes drizzled in a decadent garlic butter, this meal ticks all the boxes!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
